        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-12">
                    <div class="forty-heading">
                        <h2>View Our Domes</h2>
                        <p>
                            Take a closer look at our beautifully designed domes and start planning your relaxing Back Forty Glamping escape.
